[font=Georgia][size=5][b]DESCRIPTION:[/b][/size][/font]

A cozy little bungalow in the reach, Just a stones throw from Deep Folk Crossing Map Marker is Visible and you can travel there...Its has one bed, Crafting Cook Pot, Alchemy and Enchanting Table Tops...Also has Soul gem, Ingredients, Potion and Poison Storage Chests...Outside is a Armor Workbench, Anvil, Tanning Rack, and Sharping Wheel and Storage Chest there is also a Hen house with 6 Chickens and a Stable...Outdoor Lighting Turns off during the daylight hours...I always liked going to this location Its right in the middle of Chose Forsworn, Bandits, Dragon's  ect..So I decided why not build there!

Added additional lighting for those who find the original house to dark inside...I found the original to my liking,,,

Notice the frames on the paintings do not open fully on Low settings, at least not for me , they are silver.....

Map Marker is Visible and can be Traveled to.....

As Always, My Images are pretty bad, My computer settings are set on lowest setting.....


[font=Georgia][size=5]REQUIRED:
[/size][/font]
Latest update of Skyrim..



[font=Georgia][size=5]INSTALL:
[/size][/font]
Just unpack and drop files into your Skyrim Data FolderIf you enjoy please endorse!


[size=4]Thanks goes out to Everyone who downloaded and Endorsed my Mod :)[/size]
